{"tid":736677,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"科企被爆請人扮人工智能　咁都得？","createTime":"2018-07-10T11:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T12:34:38.000Z","uid":174649,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"083a26037d88b18e60172a7ef3dace01102fd7fd","tid":736677,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180710/photo/bkn-20180710170158404-0710_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180710174019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180710%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180710170158404-0710_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180710174019&h=0903e3e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國傳媒報道，有科技行業人士承認他們對外宣稱的「人工智能」服務，背後實際是由人手來處理。<br />\n<br />\n本月初爆出的Gmail洩露疑雲揭示了行業的「潛規則」，一些基於Gmail的第三方App允許員工閱讀用戶的郵件。涉事公司解釋，這樣做是為了改進軟件算法，訓練人工智能系統，工程師們只是「偶爾查看用戶的電子郵件」，也就是讓工程師輔助人工智能。<br />\n<br />\n「輔助人工智能」暫且可以自圓其說，但早前有報道踢爆，<a href=\"http://創業公司X.ai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8X.ai&d=hFCwhsiXD8p2qbGD2KRdAcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=87ed1857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">創業公司X.ai</a>推出的「人工智能私人助理」Amy背後實際是一支不眠不休的人工團隊，他們假扮Amy幫助用戶完成會議安排和發送電子郵件等簡單任務。<br />\n<br />\n科技公司弄虛作假除了是為了塑造行業翹楚形象外，更多是為了吸引關注和投資。有業內人士曾開玩笑說：如何創辦一家AI公司？第1，僱一群低薪者假扮AI；第2，等待AI被開發出來。"},{"pid":"e38ee4b15c223b7c7909eb4b91e3aca39b7c27ea","tid":736677,"uid":26553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"幾百年前 第一部電腦都係人扮捉棋.... <br />\n歷史不斷重演"},{"pid":"77d05d0690523b316b67557d699ea7af34db7385","tid":736677,"uid":45393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"收左人工既智能"},{"pid":"953b7c4c9a6f2044016d7f4d97639b3d95bfb966","tid":736677,"uid":67551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"以為中國醜聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82f3ba3680e524e6c01a23ca661d54fb9c58bf5","tid":736677,"uid":179938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"ATM、汽水機咪又係人扮"},{"pid":"172cdc1456593a5af06fbbb0e7e18447923be9de","tid":736677,"uid":73412,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d82f3ba3680e524e6c01a23ca661d54fb9c58bf5","tid":736677,"uid":179938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"ATM、汽水機咪又係人扮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"仲有水機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}